":307632,"uid":87281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:36:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1b3fe5b949f6271f1212acbab6846fe449171e9","tid":307632,"uid":87281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7421b3d8d0ae7eb611d0596692424c6249924af","tid":307632,"uid":126371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>btw 呢個牌子垃圾到咁 咩會有假野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位新手唔好比佢水 如果真係有3000幾筆直 我可以介紹下比佢好既結他 留tg比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想借位Sell自己可以直接啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪傻啦 我係見你賣野都<span style=\"color: red;\">咁撚臭串</span>先出聲<br />\n<br />\n如果涉及任何直接或間接個人利益既 本人不得好死</blockquote><br />\n推下po都得罪你有咩好講<br />\n<br />\n上面我指其他巴打9up個度，真心想知比係你又會點應而唔臭串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfb49958c9cd29757275d9ef856a1f7eb50cf03","tid":307632,"uid":87281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83ebe3ca88597f79fd70bed4b934f044c7a3f4c6","tid":307632,"uid":126371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各種新手唔好比佢呃 佢呢支唔係手工結他來 手工結他 起碼一萬起跳的 <br />\n勿當水魚</blockquote><br />\n原來你連po都冇追，前幾頁有木工親筆簽名張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由ALL in taylor 已經睇得出，C兄好打極有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8c483cb86a29dce54c4a054660763e39a67730","tid":307632,"uid":87281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}